description.en-US: You're gonna need a bigger boat. There's no place like home. Frankly, my dear, I don't give a damn. Toto, I've a feeling we're not in Kansas anymore. To infinity and beyond! Here's looking at you, kid.

I'm also just a girl, standing in front of a boy, asking him to love her. The Dude abides. Here's Johnny! Just when I thought I was out, they pull me back in. Elementary, my dear Watson. Gentlemen, you can't fight in here! This is the war room! I'm the king of the world!
